sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Registration - Person - Client
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant RegisterS as Register Service
    participant DB_Users as Users DB

    Client->>Gateway: POST /register (user details)
    Gateway->>RegisterS: Forward registration request
    RegisterS->>RegisterS: Validate user data
    RegisterS->>DB_Users: Save user information
    DB_Users-->>RegisterS: User created
    RegisterS-->>Gateway: Registration successful
    Gateway-->>Client: 201 Created (user details)
